## Remarks  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-538"><xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> 类在 [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)]中已过时。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-538">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> class is obsolete in [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)].</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-539">您可以通过使用 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings> 类和 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> 方法来创建验证 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> 实例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-539">You can create a validating <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> instance by using the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings> class and the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-540">有关详细信息，请参阅 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> 引用页的“备注”部分。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-540">For more information, see the Remarks section of the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> reference page.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-541">在调用 <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.MoveToAttribute%2A> 读取组成特性值的文本或实体引用节点后，请使用此方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-541">Use this method after calling <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.MoveToAttribute%2A> to read through the text or entity reference nodes that make up the attribute value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-542">属性值节点的 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Depth%2A> 是属性节点的深度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-542">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Depth%2A> of the attribute value nodes is one plus the depth of the attribute node.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-543">当你单步执行和跳出常规实体引用时，`Depth` 会递增1。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-543">The `Depth` increments and decrements by one when you step into and out of general entity references.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-544">例如，假设您具有以下 XML： `<test name="a &b; c"/>`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-544">For example, suppose you have the following XML: `<test name="a &b; c"/>`</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-545">其中，实体 `b` 在文档类型定义（DTD）中定义，如下所示： `<!ENTITY b "123">`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-545">where the entity `b` is defined in the document type definition (DTD) as follows: `<!ENTITY b "123">`</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-546">如果 <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.EntityHandling%2A> 设置为 `ExpandCharEntities`，则以下C#代码会将属性值作为两个文本节点和一个实体引用节点返回：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-546">If <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.EntityHandling%2A> is set to `ExpandCharEntities`, the following C# code returns the attribute value as two text nodes and one entity reference node:</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
reader.MoveToAttribute("name");  
  while (reader.ReadAttributeValue())  
  {  
  if (reader.NodeType == XmlNodeType.Text)  
  {  
  // at this point reader.Value == "a " or " c"  
  }  
  else if (reader.NodeType == XmlNodeType.EntityReference)  
  {  
  // at this point reader.Name == "b"  
  reader.ResolveEntity();  
  while (reader.ReadAttributeValue() &&  
  reader.NodeType != XmlNodeType.EndEntity)  
  {  
  // reader.Value == "123"  
  }  
  }  
    }  
```  
  
   
  
