## Remarks  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-731"><xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> 类在 [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)]中已过时。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-731">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> class is obsolete in [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)].</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-732">您可以通过使用 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings> 类和 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> 方法来创建验证 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> 实例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-732">You can create a validating <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> instance by using the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings> class and the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-733">有关详细信息，请参阅 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> 引用页的“备注”部分。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-733">For more information, see the Remarks section of the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> reference page.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-734">用户需要测试返回的类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-734">The user needs to test for the returned type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-735">例如，应用于对象的</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-735">For example,</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
object obj = vreader.SchemaType;  
 if (obj is XmlSchemaType)  
 {  
   XmlSchemaType st = (XmlSchemaType)obj;  
   // use XmlSchemaType object  
 }  
 if (obj is XmlSchemaDatatype)  
 {  
   XmlSchemaDatatype sd = (XmlSchemaDatatype)obj;  
   Type vt = sd.ValueType;  
   // use XmlSchemaDatatype object  
       }  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-736">如果正在执行 XML 架构验证，则 `XmlSchemaType` 或 `XmlSchemaDatatype` 对应于正在读取的当前元素。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-736">If XML Schema validation is being performed, the `XmlSchemaType` or `XmlSchemaDatatype` corresponds to the current element being read.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-737">如果正在执行文档类型定义（DTD 验证），则此属性将返回 `null`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-737">If document type definition (DTD validation) is being performed, this property returns `null`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-738">如果当前元素或特性是一个简单类型，它可以指定对简单类型的特殊验证约束（如 min 和 max），则返回 `XmlSchemaDatatype`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-738">`XmlSchemaDatatype` is returned if the current element, or attribute, is a simple type that can specify special validation constraints on the simple types, like min and max.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-739">如果当前元素或属性是用户定义的 simpleType，则返回 `XmlSchemaSimpleType`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-739">`XmlSchemaSimpleType` is returned if the current element, or attribute, is a user defined simpleType.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-740">如果当前元素是用户定义的 complexType，则返回 `XmlSchemaComplexType`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-740">`XmlSchemaComplexType` is returned if the current element is a user defined complexType.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-741">特性无法返回此类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-741">This type cannot be returned by attributes.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-742">如果 <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.ValidationType%2A> 已设置为 ValidationType，则不会从架构或 Dtd 提供任何数据类型信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-742">If <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.ValidationType%2A> has been set to ValidationType.None, no data type information is provided from either schemas or DTDs.</span></span>  
  
> [!CAUTION]
>  <span data-ttu-id="8c79c-743">调用 <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.Close%2A>后，SchemaType 将返回 Null。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8c79c-743">After calling <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.Close%2A>, SchemaType will return Null.</span></span>  
  
   
  
